title: Basmati Indian Cuisine
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Buffet, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian food place in Woodbridge Shopping Ctr. The daily buffet usually includes 4 to 6 vegetarian dishes, vegan soup, and at least 2 vegan suitable dishes which are labeled; sometimes makes a dish with tofu instead of paneer. Chef will make a dish veg upon request.
